uage-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.clip-circle</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">clip-path</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">circle</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>50% at center<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"아래가-뾰족한-세모\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%95%84%EB%9E%98%EA%B0%80-%EB%BE%B0%EC%A1%B1%ED%95%9C-%EC%84%B8%EB%AA%A8\" aria-label=\"아래가 뾰족한 세모 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>아래가 뾰족한 세모</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.clip-polygon</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">clip-path</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">polygon</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>0% 0%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 100% 0%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 50% 100%<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"항아리-모양\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%AD%EC%95%84%EB%A6%AC-%EB%AA%A8%EC%96%91\" aria-label=\"항아리 모양 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header 